        <updateDate>2020-06-08T18:34:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Investor Choice Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits broker-dealers and investment advisers from including mandatory arbitration, forum selection restrictions, or bans on class action suits in a customer or client agreement. Issuers of securities are also prohibited from mandating arbitration in a shareholder agreement.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
